  "4bf7e0e4f9107d147134aa439d338e98": "Okubhalwe ngasentla kwekhasi",
  "c5a3071b374126d5c20a3f21ebf61b10": "Inyaniso NgeAfrika",
  "e57fbbd2e433e6f6755ee1b083173826": "What if Ndikuxelele",
  "755e1a4c7f7b8bdb05b55e2105c03482": "IAfrika isiTyebi?",
  "a2aa9760aac0b9a545442d81ce04f901": "Hayi nje kwiiminerali kunye nemithombo, kodwa ngaphakathi",
  "5f44065405d41eb279fc0b5e142c7c4e": "abantu abanetalente",
