  "f22f29f8be85a62352a380e7707642b2": "I-60% yomhlaba olimekayo",
  "07cd9f71a0ec20925d047c7b038cb757": "Inkcubeko",
  "aeaad08d35d325ee5bd40092f7903174": "Ubutyebi beNkcubeko",
  "ee0e0c8a6add09ebb68fd35f617d6480": "Iilwimi ezingama-2,000+, iintlanga ezingama-54",
  "34168356b32fe52dc90ee41458f8b3ae": "Isiteyithimenti soxanduva",
  "43135c125eccb2c66241368cfae68796": "Injongo yethu",
  "8fe825914d356cf4f5952efa78371a62": "Sitshintsha indlela yaseAfrika",
  "b5a9c6e03ff944a7b509d346e2e55311": "isebenza",
  "3fc8bac97af1ff730ec4fa5b01a4e17f": "ucinga",
  "48f8143a15ab50ad4f124868971abefb": ", kwaye",
  "d8697a126f6f24996552dce518bc1811": "iba",
  "1eb64234cdee8befca5665388de3b1b2": "Ukusuka eCairo, eYiputa ukuya eKapa, ​​eMzantsi Afrika - sakha iziseko ezingundoqo zokuvula obona butyebi bukhulu baseAfrika: abantu bayo.",
  "f5e3fd4fa7a45a4563e33ae1f3940e41": "Iintlanga",
  "095470ad60e3294796b1e2aa6024f933": "Abantu",
  "e9bc44aaac9d8cc4c0fbc008aa7de841": "Okunokwenzeka",
  "72e4b2fc211e94fa8e8ea7190a8bd2e6": "═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\nINGXAKI\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════",
  "c1a30f55e8a0d455d1459b580bbec09f": "Isihloko seNgxaki",
  "fe8e09e036d1b97ef1bd2c9e03b4d791": "Italente enkulu,",
  "507634851178ea4fc90c371967439655": "Inkqubo eyaphukileyo",
  "aae7143fb4b94b4901be393fa8b9f372": "Ingxaki esiyiSombululayo",
  "4ea65ff3c516375b93ea52e5089af1bc": "Yonke imihla, izigidi zabantu baseAfrika abanetalente bavuka bekulungele ukusebenza, bekulungele ukufaka isandla, bekulungele ukutshintsha ubomi babo.\nKodwa kukho into emana ukubathintela.Ayizozakhono zabo.Yinkqubo.",
  "a07c0db4f0a3d02e69e41f512fcfc84b": "Amakhadi eNgxaki",
  "1a0d0a872b831feab6eb192dbd39675d": "Ikhadi 1: Ukungaqeshwa",
  "4cab22a3dd859ef29ced5b07508f1d80": "Ingxaki Yolutsha Lwentswela-ngqesho",
  "b8cc6a6781b11e9e9910bd9d9151a1ad": "Ngaphezu kwesiqingatha solutsha lwama-Afrika aluphangeli okanye lubambekile kwimisebenzi engasebenzisi izakhono zalo zokwenyani.\nNgawo amakhulu ezigidi zabantu abanamaphupha, izidanga, kunye nokuzimisela - kodwa akukho ndlela icacileyo eya phambili.",
  "70ec9dece9032367e382a43082f67004": "Ikhadi 2: Ingxaki yeCV",
  "fd1f7ca092117f568c33ca20a7e93ed7": "I-CV yakho ayilibali ibali lakho",
  "53401c6282f04cbe21e89aaef40083fb": "Uxwebhu olunephepha elinye elabhalwa kwiminyaka eyadlulayo alinakukubonisa ukuba ungubani kanye kanye.\nAyinakubonisa izakhono zakho zokusombulula iingxaki, ubuchule bakho, okanye indlela ophatha ngayo uxinzelelo.\nIzakhono zakho zokwenyani zihlala zifihliwe.",
  "0f2b0d244d7d1befdd073d3258a616ca": "Ikhadi 3: Imiba yokuThemba",
  "9ef77f9b65901099f32f23e1eadf0fcd": "Ukuthembela Kunzima Ukwakha",
  "1b37a9dae8e5a6b02712f55b4d352437": "Izatifikethi zomgunyathi zikuyo yonke indawo.Ii-CV ezibaxiweyo zixhaphakile.\nOku kwenza abaqeshi bakrokrele wonke umntu - nkqu nabantu abanyanisekileyo, abasebenza nzima njengawe.\nAbalungileyo bayabandezeleka ngenxa yabambalwa abaqhathayo.",
  "19be77bd69e6d29571169fc19a87016d": "Ikhadi 4: Izithintelo zeJografi",
  "314f5b572c37f6b7107f7127e8e03cc7": "Amathuba Ahlale Engingqini",
  "a1928442f13e76210ec93a73883e9a16": "Amathuba amakhulu akhoyo kwiAfrika iphela, kodwa awukhe uve ngawo.\nInkampani yaseGhana idinga izakhono zakho.Ukuqala eKenya kufuna umntu ofana nawe.\nKodwa akukho ndlela ilula yokudibanisa.",
  "0f34581ff2efd0f37eabba70e75efbed": "Ikhadi lesi-5: ISuti kunye neNtsomi yeqhina",
  "d401c67030f0c431ab4353e2d325696d": "I \"Suit & Tie\" intsomi",
  "6a061d3699eea7ce61242cc3bb17f4b5": "Uninzi lwethu lukhule lukholelwa ukuba impumelelo ithetha umsebenzi wedesika eofisini enxibe isuti.\nSiyalibala ukuba izakhono zethu zokwenyani - ukupheka, ukulima, ukwenza, ukwakha, ukudala - zixabiseke ngokufanayo.\nIhlabathi lifuna into onokuyenza ngokwenene, kungekhona nje into ekhangeleka \"ingcali.\"",
  "8eac14432b08a1ade79f423f9513c08c": "Ikhadi lesi-6: Izakhono azixatyiswanga",
  "48dfc3b858e769a2b32961a18009362c": "Izakhono eziSebenzayo azinanzwa",
  "89a25623eba1b026f8b2e158a5234d16": "Usenokuba ngumkhandi omangalisayo, umthungi onesiphiwo, umlimi onobuchule, okanye igcisa elinobuchule.\nKodwa ngenxa yokuba ezi zingezi \"nedigri,\" zihlala zingahoywa.\nUqoqosho luyaphulukana.Ulahlekelwa.Lixesha lokutshintsha oko.",
  "3e13317ec9c48d3bd73dd6dea0608187": "Eyona Ngxaki Inkcazo",
  "3f2cc444cca1b04c915cacb28896ec0f": "Nantsi inyani enzima:",
  "fceb9671f8a060d26ab3ec6fd2995b6c": "Ingxaki ayinguwe.Yinkqubo apho abaqeshi bakhathalela kakhulu ukuba i-CV yakho ikhangeleka njani na kunokuba unokwenza.\nUxwebhu olufomathwe kakuhle lufumana ingqwalasela.Izakhono zokwenyani azihoywa.\nUnokuba ngoyena ubalaseleyo kwinto oyenzayo - kodwa ukuba iCV yakho \"ayibukeki ilungile,\" awusoze ulifumane ithuba lokuyingqina.",
  "ee16308eac1c3617fc15d2a196d55434": "Oko kwaphukile.",
  "51611f7762360eeb8350230ca1912e38": "Kwaye yiloo nto kanye esilapha ukuyilungisa.",
  "dc191a4f075c8bf77a3c2bcd1c0fd279": "═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\nISICOMBULULO\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════",
  "4fbbfec6fde01fbe631fc7874c60cf74": "Iheda Yesisombululo",
  "21967ac4e9c716746e79a5e1ea795aee": "Sahluke Njani",
  "f8110c4d64d63d8be9ab13a0dbd00826": "Iqonga",
  "588128f7b533be9fc5a627788ef75de1": "Yakhelwe Wena",
  "c3e2f628388ea13d96b94fe3993c0109": "Amakhadi esisombululo",
  "7e30176d0596ae6ca9cdce1262d573f5": "Asizange nje sakhe enye ibhodi yomsebenzi.Sakhe iqonga elikubona ngokwenene -\nubuchule bakho, amandla akho, ibali lakho.Nantsi indlela esiwutshintsha ngayo umdlalo.",
  "eb73304e93e6139035f905c5dd3fcc68": "Ikhadi 1: Iprofayile ecebileyo",
  "4a84a0447d47df8926f13814ba1765b9": "Bonisa iBali lakho elipheleleyo",
  "20157c50cc636fb8566295340927ea4d": "Libele iiCV ezidikayo.Layisha ipotfoliyo yakho.Rekhoda iintshayelelo zevidiyo.\nYabelana ngeeprojekthi zakho, izatifikethi, kunye neempumelelo.\nVumela abaqeshi babone oyena mntu - hayi nje isiqwenga sephepha.",
  "07acf34f354c1be627687841c1287731": "Ikhadi 2: Ithemba eliqinisekisiweyo",
  "871bd032e18aa4fc38bfe015aeedb7b1": "Yakha Ukuthenjwa Ngokwenene",
  "ba158c91822fae5e1b6e15614fd76fc2": "Qinisekisa izakhono zakho kunye neziqinisekiso.Yakha inqaku lokuthembana abaqeshi banokukholelwa ngokwenene.\nXa usithi unokwenza into, siyakunceda ukuba uyibonakalise.\nAbantu abanyanisekileyo ekugqibeleni babalaselisa.",
  "bff6b12e914870c7139ed73c0170bcfb": "Ikhadi lesi-3: I-Smart Matching",
  "bc10d8539a2736c9ac404a1661630efa": "Amathuba Akufumana",
  "1f70d5a01b9fba1a189408b64847acd7": "Yeka ukufaka izicelo ngobumfama kumakhulu emisebenzi.Inkqubo yethu ekrelekrele ifunda ukuba yintoni osebenza kakuhle kuyo\nkwaye ikutshatise namathuba afanelekileyo.\nImisebenzi elungileyo iza kuwe.",
  "20efb57cf5104b9e01a46ec0c1384971": "Ikhadi 4: Afrika-Banzi",
  "a41a7ea9ef782942820eb7662f8e08e3": "Qhagamshelana kwiAfrika iphela",
  "e74f08a1b8a2a7eedde5714385166d09": "Italente yakho ayikhawulelwanga yimida.Ukufikelela kumathuba kuwo onke amazwe angama-54 aseAfrika\nnangaphaya.Inkampani yaseMzantsi Afrika, isiqalo eNigeria, iprojekthi eYiputa -\nbonke bayafikeleleka ngoku.",
  "fa17b9d277d43c38b42392bf87b53194": "Ikhadi lesi-5: Izixhobo zokuKhula",
  "16c46ff9c80874704f96a200e0a3baad": "Khulisa iZakhono Zakho",
  "b0d2236024191ee22b2d73df08945d86": "Asikudibanisi nje nemisebenzi.Sikunceda ubengcono.\nUkufikelela kuqeqesho, iingcebiso, kunye nezixhobo zokwakha izakhono.\nNokuba ufuna ukufunda izinto ezintsha okanye ulola into oyaziyo, sikufumene.",
  "4189a3bee10b71e1ab0a40f209bf45a5": "Ikhadi 6: Uluntu",
  "7f3ddcdfafc743fa288cf17490fca52e": "Joyina iNtshukumo",
  "0f7361c32cf519cce06f86b0100a7365": "AWUKHO wedwa.Joyina amawaka eengcali zaseAfrika ezidiniweyo yinkqubo yakudala.\nSikunye, sakha into entsha - uluntu oluphakamisana phezulu\nkwaye iyayitshintsha indlela esebenza ngayo iAfrika.",
  "ae454c41d11743dfe41592f213f1fd7a": "Ikhadi 7: Izakhono phezu kweeSuti",
  "ac37962a85ded56e3c239e3868d5f4be": "Izakhono ngaphaya kweeSuti",
  "77b30e7c79cf22f1867a327cdad5b213": "Asikhathali nokuba unxiba ntoni na.Siyakhathala ngento onokuyenza.\nNokuba ungumchweli, umbhaki, umchweli, okanye umchweli - ukuba unezakhono, ungowalapha.\nUmsebenzi wokwenyani awukho malunga nokujonga ubuchwephesha.Imalunga nokuba nexabiso.",
  "bc32a65f605bb9e4d19c225391f15c69": "Ikhadi lesi-8: Sonke iSakhono sibala",
  "718d8ede1fe5cf643bef7bf0d2f96de3": "Sonke iSakhono sinexabiso",
  "f5f5ff82224785d3030a62c781c52c8e": "Umlimi owondla amawaka.Igcisa elidala ubuhle.Umkhandi ogcina izithuthi zibaleka.\nEzi zakhono zomeleza uqoqosho lweAfrika yonke imihla.\nSilapha ukuze siqinisekise ukuba bafumana ukuqondwa - kunye namathuba - okubafaneleyo.",
  "6726cd1ab8f5a81c8942809f40a6de1b": "Isithembiso",
  "08a08431b204af9c470823877ce5fabb": "Isithembiso sethu kuwe",
  "b2c113e89b960b6d747d7f44473dc8e5": "Asithethi nje ngotshintsho — siyalwakha.Ukuba unezakhono kunye nokulambela ukukhula,\nsiya kulwela ukuqinisekisa ukuba umhlaba uyakubona.Hayi imvelaphi yakho.Hayi imidibaniso yakho.",
  "c4e76dc4ca581c8e41f1aeda94ec471f": "Wena.",
  "f6824e31256917ce9b494740eefb6ec8": "Italente yakho ifanelwe yinqanaba.Siyakha.",
  "cff650fbb176ba27b59a44823f78643d": "═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\nIINDLELA EZIMBINI CTA\n════════════════════════════════════════════════════",
  "66b02db917b690864dcc0b9671f57435": "Ukulungele ukuTshintsha",
  "1b0acada2ec96c2c2590583ff52ae3c0": "Ikamva Lakho?",
  "943cbc87a7bfcb9394821bd1eef9f4a3": "Joyina amawaka akha ikamva leAfrika.Yenza iprofayile yakho yasimahla kwimizuzu emi-2.",
