  "7fbb22f4cab09120163026d4ff5280b6": "Ukucacisa",
  "496132c09461d813ee39d0e6073b28fd": "Ixesha elide kakhulu, italente yase-Afrika ibingahoywa, ingaxatyiswanga, kwaye ifakwe kwiinkqubo eziphelelwe lixesha\nabangakwaziyo ukuqonda amandla okwenene.Silapha ukuze silibhale kwakhona elo bali.",
