  "a3bcf2c7a239c859437201aa58cd3c7c": "IAfrika likhaya",
  "dd1f7ac5cf750dd63874f2707b833e80": "I-1.4 yezigidigidi zabantu",
  "96945adef942d8bbad19f2c14e313b0c": "kunye\nitalente engaqhelekanga, ukuyila, kunye namabhongo.Ukanti, iinkqubo zesithethe ziye zasilela\nukubamba kunye nokubonisa obu buchule.",
  "ad24e88663fddc2a6b5fb97c6aa609f1": "Saqala iForgeForth Africa kuba sikholelwa ukuba ikho",
  "4b9b5dd2d9a00c91931824eec4f07da5": "amandla angaphaya kweCV engalunganga",
  "6854855579e8ffa1804f9add796dfd02": ".\nUxwebhu olunye alukwazi ukubamba iminyaka yamava, izakhono ezifundwe emsebenzini,\nokanye umlilo oqhubela umntu ukuba aphumelele.",
  "e2d9dd30495538c14b55c05d11841cf9": "Iqonga lethu lisebenzisa i-AI ukuqonda umfanekiso opheleleyo wazo zonke iingcali,\nukubadibanisa namathuba ahambelana ngokwenene namandla abo, hayi nje\niziqinisekiso zabo.",
  "1d6d50cb86afdfaa638768996b91620a": "Umseki ucaphulo",
  "bda4b5df8796659a26a6074bb47ce2dc": "\"Kukho amandla angaphaya kwe-CV engalunganga. Sibona amandla apho abanye babona iphepha.\"",
  "2d7aa446b6b1368e26b1330131ba1cf8": "- Iqela leForgeForth",
