  "63c791f5e8067000f1b875c55c0da2ae": "Ukuya",
  "6a9a5c2761e3696b5dfde766c277c396": "ukuxhobisa zonke iingcali zaseAfrika",
  "e8c41f1c20b1e7f5d0e8ec97c85efe96": "ukuya\nkhula, uqhagamshele, kwaye uphumelele ngokubonelela ngezixhobo ezikrelekrele ezibonisa ubunyani bazo\nezinokubakho kwaye uzidibanise namathuba anentsingiselo.",
  "5f6c222709e0031e408f1a388e39918a": "Qhagamshela italente namathuba ehlabathi",
  "97645ab9ad618b8ea3b8e4fa95c43145": "Ukubonelela ngezixhobo zomsebenzi eziqhutywa nge-AI",
  "6e15966e3bdc1bc8f8040f741ec5a2fa": "Yakha iiprofayili zobungcali eziqinisekisiweyo",
